{"tid":1533044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角就包抄 現場快水","createTime":"2019-09-02T16:04:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T16:43:14.000Z","uid":57073,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"573035ddf769deff024831ffa6c194a10b858102","tid":1533044,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:04:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/md5srhA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmd5srhA.jpg&h=bba93aee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2359 旺角站匯豐落狗 包抄警告 請廣傳<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkmap.live/m/476159570\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmap.live%2Fm%2F476159570&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgQKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=24a89e0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkmap.live/m/476159570</a>"},{"pid":"7b80569cec7dddaa907f0a780a92fea8130ab679","tid":1533044,"uid":132497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:05:05.000Z","msg":"希望有人幫手統籌<br />\n<br />\n[創舉] 10月1日，香港人要搞個健力士世界紀錄<br />\n<br />\n如果個日全香港人舉唔同國家既國旗，唯獨是無中共垃圾旗，搞個健力士世界紀錄，有無得諗<br />\n<br />\n香港人要入健力士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落佢鬼國面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[Record breaking] Oct 1, HongKongers need to break a Guiness World Record<br />\n<br />\nIf all the HongKongers carry different countries national flags, except the one of CCP, and break a Guiness World Record, sound good?<br />\n<br />\nHongKongers need to break a Guiness World Record<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLose ChiNazi&rsquo;s face<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532234\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532234</a>"},{"pid":"46aaa48ad02624499b25eeb9b1d2e25f447a4e4b","tid":1533044,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:05:45.000Z","msg":"be wate4"},{"pid":